Text.valUnicode: OCA200 Client info - 4. Payments - Branch totals

ExpSyntax.val: MlsTrans ('OCA200 Client info - 4. Payments - Branch totals')&':'&' '&Trim ({2,5})

SQL_STMT_U.val: select CMON_YEAR, CMON_MONTH, cast(sum(CMON_TOTAPAYCR) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTNPAYMAN) as decimal (9,0)), cast(sum(CMON_TOTNPAYAUTO) as decimal (9,0)), cast(sum(CMON_TOTRECEIVEDFROMCLIENT) as decimal(13,2)) from :1 where CLNT101_ADMNO = :6 and CMON_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and CMON_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and CLNT802_TRADECATEGORYHELLER = :2 and CMON_CURRENCY =':3' and CMON_YEAR between :4 and :5 group by CMON_YEAR, CMON_MONTH for fetch only optimize for 100 rows
